                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Taylor</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-11-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 5, 1896</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Minister for foreign affairs says that as Captain-General of Cuba reports
                    Chaqueilo taken with arms in his hands he will be tried by ordinary war
                    jurisdiction under protocol 1877.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Taylor.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
